  m_Name: Chap5
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::LevelStoryData
  levelName: 
  introLines:
  - speaker: Arin
    text: "\u0111\xE3 th\xEAm 3 ng\xE0y tr\xF4i qua r\u1ED3i m\u1ECDi ng\u01B0\u1EDDi
      c\u0169ng v\u1EABn ch\u01B0a  tr\u1EDF v\u1EC1\u2026 tr\u1EDDi h\xF4m nay s\u01B0\u01A1ng
      c\u0169ng d\xE0y th\u1EADt\u2026 L\u01B0\u01A1ng th\u1EF1c c\u0169ng d\u1EA7n
      c\u1EA1n r\u1ED3i\u2026 Shadow \xE0 ta c\xF3 1 suy ngh\u0129 ch\u1EAFc l\xE0\u2026\r\n"
  - speaker: Shadow
    text: "g\xE2u g\xE2u !"
  - speaker: Arin
    text: "l\u0169 kh\u1ED1n khi\u1EBFp \u0111\xF3 c\u1EE9 xu\u1EA5t hi\u1EC7n m\xE3i
      v\u1EADy , \u0111\xE3 th\u1EBF ng\xE0y c\xE0ng qu\xE1i d\u1ECB h\u01A1n n\u1EEFa
      ch\u1EE9"
  outroLines:
  - speaker: Arin
    text: "\u0110\u01B0\u1EE3c r\u1ED3i  Shadow ,ta quy\u1EBFt \u0111\u1ECBnh r\u1ED3i
      , ch\xFAng ta ph\u1EA3i \u0111i th\xF4i, ch\xFAng ta kh\xF4ng th\u1EC3 n\xE0o
      \u1EDF y\xEAn \u0111\xE2y ch\u1ECBu ch\u1EBFt \u0111\u01B0\u1EE3c , ch\xFAng 
      ta ph\u1EA3i t\xECm ra ngu\u1ED3n g\u1ED1c c\u1EE7a th\u1EE9 ch\u1EBFt ti\u1EC7t
      \u0111\xF3 m\u1EDBi \u0111\u01B0\u1EE3c"
  - speaker: Shadow
    text: "g\xE2u g\xE2u !"
